<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span> صحيح - انظر ما قبله.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ أَبُو حَاتِمٍ:</span> <span class="c2">(عَسَى)</span> مِنَ اللَّهِ وَاجِبٌ و <span class="c2">(أرجو)</span> مِنَ النَّبِيِّ حَقٌّ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>